Description: A new Turbo Duel hero named Yusei Fudo emerges from the outskirts of New Domino City and he will defeat any challenger thanks to his custom-built Duel Runner.
Title: YU-GI-OH 5D'S, VOL. 5
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato
Contributor: by Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato

Description: In this latest volume, Naruto battles Tobi, who has brought the demonic Gedo statue to life.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 63
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, Mikasa and Armi must learn the identity of the female Titan before she kills again.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 8
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Blood Dupre is the leader of Wonderlandâ€™s mafia and he can handle anything. Except for Alice Lidell!
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS: THE MAD HATTER'S LATE NIGHT TEA PARTY, VOL. 1
Author: QuinRose and Riko Sakura

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Tomoko Kuroki comes to a harsh realization when she begins high school: she's horribly unpopular!
Title: NO MATTER HOW I LOOK AT IT, IT'S YOU GUYS' FAULT I'M NOT POPULAR!, VOL. 1
Author: Nico Tanigawa

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?

Author: Yana Toboso

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?

Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 17
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Max and the Flock travel to Antarctica to help a group of environmental scientists studying the affects of global warming.
Title: MAXIMUM RIDE: THE MANGA, VOL. 7
Author: James Patterson and NaRae Lee
Contributor: by James Patterson and NaRae Lee
